{"3558230": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "異常進化", "steam_appid": 3558230, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mutavolve is a game that blends 3D adult content with roguelike combat mechanics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/8ccfb57b74f0bdc671ee5f57d707b2f2.poster.avif?t=1775540071\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/8ccfb57b74f0bdc671ee5f57d707b2f2.webm?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/8ccfb57b74f0bdc671ee5f57d707b2f2.mp4?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will guide the  girls through <strong>intense</strong> and <strong>thrilling battles</strong> as you fight your way forward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/3bb14a406e38c310916fbf1348cef84e.poster.avif?t=1775540071\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/3bb14a406e38c310916fbf1348cef84e.webm?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/3bb14a406e38c310916fbf1348cef84e.mp4?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you fail a challenge, you can gradually <strong>upgrade your abilities</strong> and grow stronger over time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/64f69cd552a2dd541bcdf042d6f2b770.avif?t=1775540071\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Outside of combat, you can <strong>change their outfits</strong> or <strong>engage in more intimate interactions.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/40ea802b120a52915e4a9a1627f238b0.poster.avif?t=1775540071\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/40ea802b120a52915e4a9a1627f238b0.webm?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/40ea802b120a52915e4a9a1627f238b0.mp4?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/e597006faa3c7d38e8dbc3e0c36fd282.poster.avif?t=1775540071\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/e597006faa3c7d38e8dbc3e0c36fd282.webm?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/e597006faa3c7d38e8dbc3e0c36fd282.mp4?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Current Early Access version includes:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 playable character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 replayable combat stage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skin system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unlockable animated reward scenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade System</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The current version is still limited in overall content, but the <strong>core experience is already playable</strong> and actively expanding. The following features will be added progressively:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More characters and interaction content</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wider variety of skills and build options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New enemies, stages, and gameplay mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More animated rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanded progression systems</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visual and performance improvements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mutavolve is being developed through Early Access with a focus on <strong>continuous improvement based on player feedback.</strong> Your feedback will directly shape the future of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have any thoughts or encounter any issues, feel free to share them through the community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will continue to <strong>evolve and grow throughout Early Access.</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mutavolve is a game that blends 3D adult content with roguelike combat mechanics.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/8ccfb57b74f0bdc671ee5f57d707b2f2.poster.avif?t=1775540071\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/8ccfb57b74f0bdc671ee5f57d707b2f2.webm?t=1775540071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3558230/extras/8ccfb57b74f0bdc671ee5f57d707b2f2.mp4